{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Give all UK citizens access to their pension pots immediately tax free.",
        "additional_details": "The Government will need to borrow to support every part of the economy and individuals/ families through these challenging times with the coronavirus. Many of us have pensions but are not able to access these and even at the age of 55 only 25% tax free. This is radical but allowing us to access 100% tax free right now will allow investment in business, continued tax receipts for Government, families to be fed, staff to keep their jobs, etc. It is a very good option.",
        "background": "Rather than borrow from the Government lets utilise these pension funds right now. Give business and individuals the choice to back themselves.",
